    "detail": "location is perfect. Walking distance from the TRA and the intercity bus terminals. Bus stops going to different attractions in taichung like Fengjia and yizhong market are also walking distance from the hotel (one literally in front of the hotel). check-in and check out is a breeze since it is automated (first time I've tried it). Staff are friendly, can speak good English and always ready to assist you. room is small but enough for us. it is also very clean with complete toiletries. buffet breakfast is adequate for its price. some dishes are actually delicious. Overall, this is really a great hotel in taichung with value for money. will stay again here in our next visit to taichung. Thanks Chance.",
